    "description": "Pangaroids is a small retro arcade shooter with simple mechanics, designed for the high score chaser in all of us.<br><br>Endless survival score chasing gameplay inspired by some of our favourite arcade classics like <i>Asteroids</i> and <i>Pang</i>!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Command your ship to clear the screen of waves of enemy metal orbs.<br></li><li>Easy to learn, simple controls to turn your ship, boost, and brake. Keyboard controls – arrow keys for moving, spacebar for shooting.<br></li><li>Your ship can’t stop. Turn it left and right and use your thrust and brake to keep from crashing into enemies.<br></li><li>Shooting big orbs will cause them to split into smaller orbs. Sometimes they will release a power-up.<br></li><li>Pick up a wide variety of awesome power-ups to help you survive longer. But beware bad power-ups that speed up enemies, enlarge or slow your ship down, annoyingly reverse your controls, or encase your ship in a block of ice... making survival even more challenging. So why pick up bad power-ups? They're worth a lot more points! No risk, no reward.<br></li><li>Don't like a spawned power-up? Shoot it until it changes to something you like. That is, if you think you have enough time to pick it up...<br></li><li>Get the high score.<br></li><li>Enjoy the chip tunes.</li></ul>",
